    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s super clean inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh new-car smell! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, you\u2019ve found it. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44500.0,
