    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a whisper-quiet VANOS system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, mechanical engagement, paired with a fresh clutch and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The suspension remains taut with OEM bushings and dampers, maintaining the original handling geometry. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the interior shows negligible bolster wear on the Nappa leather. No codes, no leaks, and a comprehensive service history detailing recent rod bearing replacement. This is a collector-grade driver's machine with zero deferred maintenance.",
